query:
INSERT INTO sessions (id, name, tmux_session, created_at, last_active)
            VALUES (?1, ?2, ?3, ?4, ?5)
            RETURNING 
                id as "id!: String",
                name as "name!: String",
                tmux_session as "tmux_session?: String",
                created_at as "created_at!: NaiveDateTime",
                last_active as "last_active!: NaiveDateTime",
                metadata as "metadata?: String"
